@startuml
title Reservation / Payment To Kaze Pass Access Flow

actor Customer
participant "Venue App" as App
participant "Reservation Service" as Reservation
participant "Payment Service" as Payment
participant "Pass Service" as Pass
participant "Venue Access Control" as Access

Customer -> App : Select venue space and layout
App -> Reservation : Create quote / draft reservation
Reservation --> App : Reservation draft + price

Customer -> App : Confirm reservation
App -> Payment : Start payment
Payment --> App : Payment instructions\n(MoMo / Airtel Money / BK-RSwitch / other)

Customer -> Payment : Complete payment
Payment -> Reservation : Mark deposit or full payment
Reservation -> Pass : Generate entitlement if required
Pass -> Access : Register allowed zones / time window

App -> Pass : Fetch Kaze Pass details
Pass --> App : Pass code + access scope + status

Customer -> Access : Present Kaze Pass at entry
Access -> Pass : Validate entitlement
Pass --> Access : Valid / invalid
Access --> Customer : Allow or deny entry

note over Reservation,Pass
Pass generation may depend on:
- reservation approval
- payment state
- event rules
- guest category
end note

@enduml
